      "content": "i get that but i dont really want to deal with my doctor about this, it's such a hassle and they always just tell me to stay on the meds. i've already read a few forums where people say the herb works just as well for them. if i just taper off the sertraline over a week and then start the st johns wort, would that be safe enough? i just want to avoid the side effects.",
